subject: Baseball
lead_paragraph: The Baltimore Orioles traded Miguel Tejada to the Houston Astros on Wednesday for outfielder Luke Scott, pitchers Matt Albers, Troy Patton and Dennis Sarfate, and third baseman Michael Costanzo.
